pick up the bar of soap off the table
turn around and walk straight then turn left towards the tub then turn left again towards the table
open the table drawer and put the soap inside and close it

pick up the bar of soap in the tub

Pick up the soap on the table.

Put the soap in the drawer of the table.

Put the soap in the drawer of the table.

high_descs: Take one step forward then turn left to face the black table.
Pick up the pink bar of soap on the black table.
Turn around and take one step then turn back around to face the black table.

Pick up the bar of soap from the tub.
